WEBVTT

00:03:59.244 --> 00:04:02.219
Mum, Dad, Nan, Pop.

00:04:02.243 --> 00:04:06.183
The first two ideas on that list
create a pattern,

00:04:06.207 --> 00:04:08.422
and that pattern creates expectation.

00:04:08.446 --> 00:04:11.316
And then the third thing -- bam! --
Kayak. What?

00:04:11.340 --> 00:04:12.670
That's the rule of three.

00:04:12.694 --> 00:04:15.085
One, two, surprise! Ha ha.

00:04:15.109 --> 00:04:18.337
(Laughter)

00:04:20.851 --> 00:04:25.694
Now, the rule of three is not only
fundamental to the way I do my craft,

00:04:25.718 --> 00:04:28.375
it is also fundamental
to the way I communicate.

00:04:28.399 --> 00:04:31.033
So I won't be changing
anything for nobody,